As the World Cup 2022 starts, you can now pick which country you support and think will WIN the 2022 World Cup.

Select your team now & start ordering for a chance to WIN! 10 winners will be selected 😍 with the top 3 receiving FREE DELIVERY for A YEAR and the other 7 winners will receive 50 OMR TM DONE Credit.

\Choose the winning team and make sure to order on TM DONE! The more you order, the more loyalty points you will gain & so are your chances to WIN!

\Pick wisely & good luck!! 😁

Terms and Conditions Apply:
1. Winners will be picked after the final match of the 2022 World Cup.
2. Only those who select the winning country of the 2022 World Cup final will enter the raffle draw.
3. Once you select your team you cannot change it at a later date.
4. If your team gets disqualified, you too will get disqualified from entering the raffle draw.
5. Loyalty Points for the raffle will only be calculated from the day you pick your team, previous loyalty points will not be considered.
6. Loyalty points will only be added for completed orders, not cancelled orders.
7. If you have 0 Loyalty Points by the end of the 2022 World Cup you will not be eligible to enter the draw.
8. Only Omani Citizens & Residents are eligible to enter the draw.
9. Free delivery will be provided for 3 orders per day for a period of a year from the date of winning.
